So if you've not yet confessed Jesus is Lord, I urge you to call in His name and believe that He is the Son of God who died for our sins and rose from the dead.

27:25.989 --> 27:28.913
And then the Bible promises, you shall be saved.

27:29.254 --> 27:33.419
And also you'll be ready for the soon and sudden appearing of the Lord.

27:33.880 --> 27:35.422
And that's our blessed hope.

27:35.442 --> 27:35.763
Amen.

27:36.944 --> 27:41.170
I'd love to hear from you on social media or through our free Jerusalem channel mobile app.

27:41.730 --> 28:01.529
Please follow all of our articles at substack.com and our videos at our Jerusalem channel, YouTube platform, as well as our website, exploits.tv, where you have the opportunity to join our every Friday fast for release of the captives and to support our broadcast and outreaches financially.

28:02.369 --> 28:07.654
Finally, we invite you to sign up for our weekly email alert called exploits based upon Daniel 1132.

28:08.655 --> 28:11.698
Declaring the people who know their God will be strong, not weak,

28:11.970 --> 28:18.306
and will accomplish biblical exploits, the works of the Lord in the remaining time before His imminent return.

28:19.129 --> 28:24.924
Let's keep contending for the faith and praying earnestly for the peace of Jerusalem and the entire region.

28:25.345 --> 28:28.914
I'm Christine Darrick, Shalom and Maranatha.

